<item>
            <title>[LU-15592] lbuild patching rhel8 kmodtool is broken</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15592</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Recent change from kmodtool broke the patch we did for lbuild. We need to evaluate if we need to patch or not; and fix it&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
09:45:57 ++ RHEL_KMODTOOL=/usr/lib/rpm/redhat/kmodtool
09:45:57 ++ LBUILD_KMODTOOL=/&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;/lib/jenkins/workspace/lustre-master/arch/x86_64/build_type/client/distro/el8.5/ib_stack/inkernel/contrib/lbuild/rhel8/kmodtool
09:45:57 ++ cp /usr/lib/rpm/redhat/kmodtool /&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;/lib/jenkins/workspace/lustre-master/arch/x86_64/build_type/client/distro/el8.5/ib_stack/inkernel/contrib/lbuild/rhel8/kmodtool
09:45:57 ++ pushd /&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;var&lt;/span&gt;/lib/jenkins/workspace/lustre-master/arch/x86_64/build_type/client/distro/el8.5/ib_stack/inkernel/contrib/lbuild/rhel8
09:45:57 ~/workspace/lustre-master/arch/x86_64/build_type/client/distro/el8.5/ib_stack/inkernel/contrib/lbuild/rhel8 ~/workspace/lustre-master/arch/x86_64/build_type/client/distro/el8.5/ib_stack/inkernel/BUILD
09:45:57 ++ patch -p1
09:45:57 patching file kmodtool
09:45:57 Hunk #1 FAILED at 62.
09:45:57 1 out of 1 hunk FAILED -- saving rejects to file kmodtool.rej
09:45:57 +++ set +x
09:45:57 An unexpected error has occurred at lbuild-rhel8:29.
09:45:57 Unfortunately the above line number in the message may or may not be correct,
09:45:57 but details have been send to the lbuild maintainer.  Attempting to &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;continue&lt;/span&gt;.
09:45:57 Untrapped error
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
